headline: 4 Stocks to Watch From the Prospering Insurance Brokerage Industry
summary: Higher demand for insurance products, strategic acquisitions and the adoption of technology should drive the performance of Zacks Insurance Brokerage industry players like BRO, MMC, AJG and WTW.
